"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/456347","Ministry of Justice","false","2016-03-15","<p>This information is not held centrally and can only be obtained at disproportionate cost.</p><p> </p><p>The National Crime Agency publishes statistics on the operation of the European Arrest Warrant. These can be found on their website.</p>",,"Lord Faulks","HL6579 ; HL6580 ; HL6582","2016-03-15T17:05:56.513Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/456347/answer","Biography information for Lord Faulks","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/456347/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/456347/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2016-03-01","European Arrest Warrants","2","House of Lords","To ask Her Majesty’s Government what is the average length of sentence of offenders sentenced after having been returned to the UK under a European Arrest Warrant.","false","Biography information for Lord Falconer of Thoroton",,"Lord Falconer of Thoroton","HL6581"
